{"thi-ap22:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap22:0.2":"Kundalakesivagga ","thi-ap22:0.3":"Kisagotamitheriapadana ","thi-ap22:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","thi-ap22:1.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","thi-ap22:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","thi-ap22:1.4":"kappe uppajji nayako. ","thi-ap22:2.1":"Tadaham hamsavatiyam, ","thi-ap22:2.2":"jata annatare kule; ","thi-ap22:2.3":"Upetva tam naravaram, ","thi-ap22:2.4":"saranam samupagamim. ","thi-ap22:3.1":"Dhammanca tassa assosim, ","thi-ap22:3.2":"catusaccupasanhitam; ","thi-ap22:3.3":"Madhuram paramassadam, ","thi-ap22:3.4":"vattasantisukhavaham. ","thi-ap22:4.1":"Tada ca bhikkhunim viro, ","thi-ap22:4.2":"lukhacivaradharinim; ","thi-ap22:4.3":"Thapento etadaggamhi, ","thi-ap22:4.4":"vannayi purisuttamo. ","thi-ap22:5.1":"Janetvanappakam pitim, ","thi-ap22:5.2":"sutva bhikkhuniya gune; ","thi-ap22:5.3":"Karam katvana buddhassa, ","thi-ap22:5.4":"yathasatti yathabalam. ","thi-ap22:6.1":"Nipacca munivaram tam, ","thi-ap22:6.2":"tam thanamabhipatthayim; ","thi-ap22:6.3":"Tadanumodi sambuddho, ","thi-ap22:6.4":"thanalabhaya nayako. ","thi-ap22:7.1":"‘Satasahassito kappe, ","thi-ap22:7.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","thi-ap22:7.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","thi-ap22:7.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","thi-ap22:8.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayada, ","thi-ap22:8.2":"orasa dhammanimmita; ","thi-ap22:8.3":"Kisagotami namena, ","thi-ap22:8.4":"hessati satthu savika’. ","thi-ap22:9.1":"Tam sutva mudita hutva, ","thi-ap22:9.2":"yavajivam tada jinam; ","thi-ap22:9.3":"Mettacitta paricarim, ","thi-ap22:9.4":"paccayehi vinayakam. ","thi-ap22:10.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","thi-ap22:10.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap22:10.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap22:10.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap22:11.1":"Imamhi bhaddake kappe, ","thi-ap22:11.2":"brahmabandhu mahayaso; ","thi-ap22:11.3":"Kassapo nama gottena, ","thi-ap22:11.4":"uppajji vadatam varo. ","thi-ap22:12.1":"Upatthako mahesissa, ","thi-ap22:12.2":"tada asi narissaro; ","thi-ap22:12.3":"Kasiraja kiki nama, ","thi-ap22:12.4":"baranasipuruttame. ","thi-ap22:13.1":"Pancami tassa dhitasim, ","thi-ap22:13.2":"dhamma namena vissuta; ","thi-ap22:13.3":"Dhammam sutva jinaggassa, ","thi-ap22:13.4":"pabbajjam samarocayim. ","thi-ap22:14.1":"Anujani na no tato, ","thi-ap22:14.2":"agareva tada mayam; ","thi-ap22:14.3":"Visavassasahassani, ","thi-ap22:14.4":"vicarimha atandita. ","thi-ap22:15.1":"Komaribrahmacariyam, ","thi-ap22:15.2":"rajakanna sukhedhita; ","thi-ap22:15.3":"Buddhopatthananirata, ","thi-ap22:15.4":"mudita satta dhitaro. ","thi-ap22:16.1":"Samani samanagutta ca, ","thi-ap22:16.2":"bhikkhuni bhikkhudayika; ","thi-ap22:16.3":"Dhamma ceva sudhamma ca, ","thi-ap22:16.4":"sattami sanghadayika. ","thi-ap22:17.1":"Khema uppalavanna ca, ","thi-ap22:17.2":"patacara ca kundala; ","thi-ap22:17.3":"Ahanca dhammadinna ca, ","thi-ap22:17.4":"visakha hoti sattami. ","thi-ap22:18.1":"Tehi kammehi sukatehi, ","thi-ap22:18.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap22:18.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap22:18.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap22:19.1":"Pacchime ca bhave dani, ","thi-ap22:19.2":"jata setthikule aham; ","thi-ap22:19.3":"Duggate adhane natthe, ","thi-ap22:19.4":"gata ca sadhanam kulam. ","thi-ap22:20.1":"Patim thapetva sesa me, ","thi-ap22:20.2":"dessanti adhana iti; ","thi-ap22:20.3":"Yada ca pasuta asim, ","thi-ap22:20.4":"sabbesam dayita tada. ","thi-ap22:21.1":"Yada so taruno bhaddo, ","thi-ap22:21.2":"komalako sukhedhito; ","thi-ap22:21.3":"Sapanamiva kanto me, ","thi-ap22:21.4":"tada yamavasam gato. ","thi-ap22:22.1":"Sokattadinavadana, ","thi-ap22:22.2":"assunetta rudammukha; ","thi-ap22:22.3":"Matam kunapamadaya, ","thi-ap22:22.4":"vilapanti gamamaham. ","thi-ap22:23.1":"Tada ekena sandittha, ","thi-ap22:23.2":"upetvabhisakkuttamam; ","thi-ap22:23.3":"Avocam ‘dehi bhesajjam, ","thi-ap22:23.4":"puttasanjivananti bho’. ","thi-ap22:24.1":"‘Na vijjante mata yasmim, ","thi-ap22:24.2":"gehe siddhatthakam tato; ","thi-ap22:24.3":"Ahara’ti jino aha, ","thi-ap22:24.4":"vinayopayakovido. ","thi-ap22:25.1":"Tada gamitva savatthim, ","thi-ap22:25.2":"na labhim tadisam gharam; ","thi-ap22:25.3":"Kuto siddhatthakam tasma, ","thi-ap22:25.4":"tato laddha satim aham. ","thi-ap22:26.1":"Kunapam chaddayitvana, ","thi-ap22:26.2":"upesim lokanayakam; ","thi-ap22:26.3":"Duratova mamam disva, ","thi-ap22:26.4":"avoca madhurassaro. ","thi-ap22:27.1":"‘Yo ca vassasatam jive, ","thi-ap22:27.2":"apassam udayabbayam; ","thi-ap22:27.3":"Ekaham jivitam seyyo, ","thi-ap22:27.4":"passato udayabbayam. ","thi-ap22:28.1":"Na gamadhammo nigamassa dhammo, ","thi-ap22:28.2":"Na capiyam ekakulassa dhammo; ","thi-ap22:28.3":"Sabbassa lokassa sadevakassa, ","thi-ap22:28.4":"Eseva dhammo yadidam aniccata’. ","thi-ap22:29.1":"Saham sutvanima gatha, ","thi-ap22:29.2":"dhammacakkhum visodhayim; ","thi-ap22:29.3":"Tato vinnatasaddhamma, ","thi-ap22:29.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","thi-ap22:30.1":"Tatha pabbajita santi, ","thi-ap22:30.2":"yunjanti jinasasane; ","thi-ap22:30.3":"Na cireneva kalena, ","thi-ap22:30.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","thi-ap22:31.1":"Iddhisu ca vasi homi, ","thi-ap22:31.2":"dibbaya sotadhatuya; ","thi-ap22:31.3":"Paracittani janami, ","thi-ap22:31.4":"satthusasanakarika. ","thi-ap22:32.1":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","thi-ap22:32.2":"dibbacakkhu visodhitam; ","thi-ap22:32.3":"Khepetva asave sabbe, ","thi-ap22:32.4":"visuddhasim sunimmala. ","thi-ap22:33.1":"Paricinno maya sattha, ","thi-ap22:33.2":"katam buddhassa sasanam; ","thi-ap22:33.3":"Ohito garuko bharo, ","thi-ap22:33.4":"bhavanetti samuhata. ","thi-ap22:34.1":"Yassatthaya pabbajita, ","thi-ap22:34.2":"agarasmanagariyam; ","thi-ap22:34.3":"So me attho anuppatto, ","thi-ap22:34.4":"sabbasamyojanakkhayo. ","thi-ap22:35.1":"Atthadhammaniruttisu, ","thi-ap22:35.2":"patibhane tatheva ca; ","thi-ap22:35.3":"Nanam me vimalam suddham, ","thi-ap22:35.4":"buddhasetthassa vahasa. ","thi-ap22:36.1":"Sankarakuta ahitva, ","thi-ap22:36.2":"susana rathiyapi ca; ","thi-ap22:36.3":"Tato sanghatikam katva, ","thi-ap22:36.4":"lukham dharemi civaram. ","thi-ap22:37.1":"Jino tasmim gune tuttho, ","thi-ap22:37.2":"lukhacivaradharane; ","thi-ap22:37.3":"Thapesi etadaggamhi, ","thi-ap22:37.4":"parisasu vinayako. ","thi-ap22:38.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap22:38.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap22:38.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap22:39.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap22:39.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap22:39.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap22:40.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap22:40.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap22:40.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap22:41.1":"Ittham sudam kisagotami bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap22:42.1":"Kisagotamitheriyapadanam dutiyam. "}